{"id": "xos033", "name": "Cam_CArea_702_11_08", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "Alarm"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Trespassers in area C, the underground passages. Send additional agents and drones immediately!</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "Door Knock"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "Door Knock"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Good evening.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "!?\nHow did you...?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "I knocked, but nobody answered the door. Therefore, I decided to come in myself. Pardon me for my intrusion.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... What the hell are you doing?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DeleteFile", "Data projection"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "I don't have time to explain all the minute details to you. All in all, take a quick look through these files first.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!!\nUGH......!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">My investigation with her... These images...</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Ho, so it actually worked? Excellent, I'm getting more and more interested... in this Æsir fellow.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "How are you feeling? Do you remember it now? The reason why you are here.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Why are you helping me?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Help you? Young man, you're mistaken. You're the one that's going to help me.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "What do you mean?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "My next step is to leave Node 08.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You're escaping? You're a criminal right now, you know.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Haha, being told you are a criminal by a guy wearing a prison uniform, how amusing.\nI've already obtained all the information I wanted to get with A.R.C. There is no reason for me to remain here anymore.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "In the end, I had to rely on myself. Judging by how terrible you look right now, you don't seem to be of much help either. That makes things a bit... tricky.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "What exactly are you trying to do?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Your memory has already recovered. Here's your mobile device. I'll put it here. Starting now, I will present you with two \"choices\". \nChoice number one, go to Node 03, meet up with me there. I will tell you many more interesting things, including things about Æsir, A.R.C., and this world itself.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Choice number two, stay here and wait for the admins to prove your innocence through the proper procedures, or be a sitting duck and await your own demise.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "I shall remind you first.\nOnce you set foot outside this door, you are, in all sense of the word, \"dead\". No one in society will ever acknowledge your existence. Your family, friends, life, and dreams will all be reduced to ashes. Nothing will be left.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "I still have more important businesses to tend to, So I don't have time to waste on you here.\nAlthough having your assistance will make things much easier for me, the final decision is all yours to make.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "Alarm"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Ah, right. Seems like we got a signal. Please give me a minute.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "This is R. Woah, looks like it's quite the spectacle on your side of things.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Cherry]"], "content": "<i>You bastard! How dare you trick me! Where the f*** am I at right now!?</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "No need to worry. I've already opened Simon's cell door. However, it seems like he doesn't really want to come out.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry!? What are you doing here?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Cherry]"], "content": "<i>……!</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "As you just saw, your dear friends are literally risking their lives for you. All in all, I will leave the door open for you, the door to end this entire fiasco. The rest is up to you.\nFeels like your dear friends are in a pretty serious pinch. Allow me to take my leave first.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "警報"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">エリアCに侵入者あり！\n人員とドローンの増員をお願いします！</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "扉を叩く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "扉を叩く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "こんばんは。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！？\nなぜここに……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "ノックをしたのだが、何も反応がなかったのでね。\n失礼は承知だが、自分で入らせてもらったよ。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……何を考えている？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DeleteFile", "データ投影"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "君に詳しい事情を説明している暇はない。\nとにかく、この資料を見てもらおう。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………！！\nグ……ッ！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">俺とあいつの調査記録……これは……</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "おや、本当に効き目があったのかね？\n素晴らしい。より興味がわいてきたよ。\nこのÆsirという奴に対してね。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "どうだね？思い出したかね？\n自分がなぜここにいるのか。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……なんで俺のために……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "君のため？\nふむ、君は何か勘違いをしているようだ。\n君のためではない。\n君が私のために働くのだよ。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "どういう意味です？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "私はNode08を離れようと思っていてね。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "逃げるつもりですか？\nあなたは罪人なんですよ。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "ははは！\n囚人服を着た輩に罪人呼ばわりされるとは、中々ユーモアが利いてるじゃないか。\nA.R.C.を利用して手に入れたい情報は全て手に入れた。\nもうここに留まり続ける理由はないのだよ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "最終的にはやはり自分の力に頼るしかない。\n君が今のようなひどい状態のままだと、困るのだよ。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "何を考えているんです。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "君の記憶はもう戻った。\nこれは君のモバイルデバイスだ。\nここに置いておこう。\n君は今2つの「選択肢」がある。\nひとつは、Node03へ行き、私と落ち合う。\nそこで、もっと面白い話をしてあげよう。\nÆsir、A.R.C.、そしてこの世界について……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "二つ目は、ここで管理局が正攻法で君の無実を証明してくれるのを待つか、もしくは死を待つか。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "先に言っておこう。\n君はこの扉をくぐった瞬間に「死んだ」ことになる。\nこの社会に君の存在を認める者はいなくなり、家族、友人、人生、夢、全てが塵となって消える。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "私にはもっと大事なやるべきことがあるのだよ。\nここで君のために時間を無駄にしている暇はない。\n君の助けがあれば、楽になることは間違いないが、全て君次第だ。\n君もこの世界の背後に隠された真相に興味があるのであれば、慎重に選択することをおすすめするよ。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "警報"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "そういえば、そろそろ電波が繋がるころだな。\n少し待っていてくれるかい。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "こちらR。\nおや、面白いことになっているようだね。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Cherry]"], "content": "ペテン師め！騙したな！\n今どこにいやがる！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "まあまあ、そう怒らないでくれたまえ。\n私は今Simonの部屋の扉を開けたところさ。\n本人はあまり出てきたくなさそうだがね。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry！？お前何して……！？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Cherry]"], "content": "<i>……！</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "君の見た通りさ。\n仲間たちは今君のために命をはっている。\nとにかく、この騒ぎをおさめるための扉はもう開いた。\nあとは、君がどうするかだ。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "警鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">C 區地下通道有人入侵，立刻增派人員與無人機！</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "晚安啊。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！？\n你怎麼……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我敲了門都沒人應門，所以我就自己進來了，失禮。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你在搞什麼鬼？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DeleteFile", "資料投影"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我沒時間跟你解釋有的沒的呢，總之你先看一下這些資料吧。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！！\n呃啊……！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我跟她的追查……這些畫面……</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "真的有用啊？很好，我越來越感興趣了，這個叫 Æsir 的傢伙。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "如何？想起來了嗎？自己為什麼會在這裡。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……為什麼要幫我？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "幫你？你搞錯了，是你要幫我才對。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "什麼意思？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我接下來要離開 Node 08 了。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "你要逃？你現在可是罪犯。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "哈哈，被一個穿著囚服的傢伙這麼叫，真幽默。\n我想利用 A.R.C. 得到的情報全都已經到手，沒有待在這的理由了。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "結果還是靠我自己，你因為現在這副慘樣一點也派不上用場，這樣下去有點困擾呢。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "你到底想幹嘛？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "你的記憶已經恢復了，這是你的行動裝置，我放在這。現在開始給你兩個「選擇」，第一、到 Node 03，在那裡跟我碰面，我會告訴你更多有趣的事情，包括 Æsir、A.R.C.、還有這個世界。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "第二、留在這裡等待管理局用正當的管道還你清白，或是等死。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我先提醒你，踏出了這個房門，你就也等於死了。社會上再也沒有任何人會承認你的存在，你的家人、朋友、人生、夢想全都會化成灰燼。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我接下來有更重要的事情要做，沒時間在這跟你耗。\n雖然有你的協助我會輕鬆不少，不過這完全取決於你。如果你也對這個世界背後的真相有點興趣，我建議你謹慎選擇。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "警鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "對了，好像有訊號了呢，稍等我一下。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "這裡是 R。哇，妳那兒看起來很精彩啊。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Cherry]"], "content": "<i>你這混蛋！居然騙我！我現在到底在哪！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "別緊張，我已經把 Simon 的房門打開了，不過他好像不太願意出來啊。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry！？妳在這做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Cherry]"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "就像你看到的，小夥伴們在為了你拼命啊。總之，結束這場鬧劇的大門我幫你開著，剩下的就看你自己了。\n你的小夥伴們感覺不太妙呢，我先告辭了。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "경보음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">C구역 지하에 침입자다! 당장 인력과 드론들을 투입시켜!</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "노크"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "노크"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "오랜만이로군요.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "!?\n당신이 여길 어떻게!?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "들어가기 전에 노크를 했는데도 아무 반응이 없어 이렇게 실례를 무릅쓰고 들어오게 됐습니다.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...대체 뭘 할 생각인 겁니까?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DeleteFile", "데이터 재생"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "지금 당신에게 자세한 상황을 설명할 시간이 없습니다만. 먼저 이 데이터를 보시죠.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "....?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!!\n크윽......!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">내가 조사했던 기록들....이 화면들은...</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "역시 효과가 있는 것 같군. 아주 잘 됐습니다. 더욱 흥미가 생기는군요. 바로 이 자가 Æsir라는 녀석입니다.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "어떻습니까? 생각해냈는지?\n자신이 왜 이곳에 있는지 말이죠.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...어째서 날 돕는 거죠?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "당신을 돕는다라...\n잘못 짚었습니다. \n정확히는 당신이 날 돕는다고 말할 수 있겠군요.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "무슨 뜻이죠?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "전 이제 Node 08을 떠날 생각입니다.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "도망가겠다고?\n당신은 지금 범죄자라고.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "하하하! 죄수복을 입고 있는 자에게 그렇게 불리다니, 나름 웃겼습니다.\nA.R.C.를 이용해서 얻을 수 있는 정보들은 이미 전부 손에 넣었거든요. 더 이상 그곳에 있을 필요는 없을 것 같아서.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "뭐, 보아하니 아직은 제 스스로 움직여야할 것 같군요. 지금 당신의 모습을 보니, 조금도 쓸모 있을 것 같지 않아서 말입니다. 흐음, 이러면 조금 곤란한데...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "대체 무슨 꿍꿍이를 꾸미고 있는 거야!?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "당신의 기억은 이미 모두 회복된 것 같군요. 당신의 모바일 장치는 이곳에 놓아두도록 하죠. \n자, 지금부터 당신에게 2가지 「선택지」를 드리겠습니다.\n우선 첫 번째. \nNode 03에서 나와 만나는 것. 그곳에서 만나면 당신께 더욱 많은 흥미로운 사실들을 말해주도록 하죠. 물론 Æsir와 A.R.C, 그리고 이 세계에 대한 것들을 포함해서 말이죠.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "두 번째. \n이곳에 남아서 관리국이 당신의 결백을 증명해줄 때까지 기다리는 것. 물론 평생 기다리다가 여기서 죽어버릴 수도 있겠지만.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "미리 말해둬야겠군요.\n이 방을 나서면, 당신은 세상에서 죽은 거나 다름없게 되는 겁니다. 이 세상에서 당신의 존재를 인정하는 자들은 모두 사라지는 거죠. 가족, 친구, 인생, 자신의 꿈까지 모두 먼지가 되어 사라지는 겁니다.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "전 이제 더욱 중요한 일을 앞두고 있어서, 당신과 더 이상 시간을 끌고 있을 여유가 없습니다.\n물론 당신의 도움이 있다면 제가 좀 편해지겠지만, 뭐 그래도 결정은 전적으로 당신에게 맡기도록 하죠.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "경보음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "이런, 신호가 온 것 같군요. 잠깐만 기다려주시죠.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "여기는 R.\n와우, 그쪽은 매우 재밌어진 것 같군요.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Cherry]"], "content": "이 x자식! 날 속이다니! 지금 여긴 대체 어디야!?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "이런, 긴장할 필요 없습니다. 전 이미 Simon의 방으로 들어왔습니다. 그런데 이 친구가 별로 나가고 싶어 하지 않는 것 같군요.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry!? \n네가 왜 여기에!?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Cherry]"], "content": "<i>……！</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "보시는 것처럼,\n동료들이 당신을 위해 목숨을 걸었습니다. 어쨌든, 당신이 이 소동으로부터 빠져나갈 수 있는 문은 모두 준비된 셈이군요. 나머지는 당신에게 달렸습니다.\n그런데 지금, 당신 동료가 약간 난처한 상황에 처한 것 같습니다만? \n그럼 전 이만.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "t